{"id": "ChIJiep1aCJ_hYAR5dNpt7Rt_zk", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 150, "displayName": {"text": "Hui Lau Shan", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJiep1aCJ_hYAR5dNpt7Rt_zk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1aFoxQnFkSEJNVW1sUk9IQXROMFJ2VWtvd2NrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Overall the mango desserts here are really good. I love the mango mochi! Recently I got the mango dessert with rice balls and it was mostly mango puree, it didn’t have enough rice balls or mango slices in my opinion. But the flavors were really good and it was refreshing. Also, their service is really fast.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Overall the mango desserts here are really good. I love the mango mochi! Recently I got the mango dessert with rice balls and it was mostly mango puree, it didn’t have enough rice balls or mango slices in my opinion. But the flavors were really good and it was refreshing. Also, their service is really fast.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jenna Tarabishy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118261438890334086775/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRC9-3i4o2cGtsudp-JPfgmU-g_bRasHcwmXubo51kSu4Uk7OM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T08:37:01.054647534Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1aFoxQnFkSEJNVW1sUk9IQXROMFJ2VWtvd2NrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1aFoxQnFkSEJNVW1sUk9IQXROMFJ2VWtvd2NrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f226875ea89:0x39ff6db4b769d3e5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiep1aCJ_hYAR5dNpt7Rt_zk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaV1oxUk9iR1JOYVdwQ1JUZGFWVTh4TFZnd2NWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I love this place! My husband and I ordered through Snackpass because it was our first time using the app, and I believe we got 5% off — though I’m not entirely sure.\n\nWe ordered the Passion Fruit Mango Icy and Mango & Coconut with Crystal Jelly, and we loved both drinks. The passion fruit mango is perfect for a hot day, especially after a heavy or oily meal — it’s so refreshing and really helps cleanse the palate. The mango & coconut is an amazing combination; the mango and crystal jelly balance out the richness of the coconut perfectly, creating a well-rounded, delicious drink that you have to try. The sweetness is just right — not too sweet, which I really appreciate.\n\nThe shop itself is quite small with limited seating, so it’s more of a pick-up-and-go spot. The service was decent — not over-the-top, but good enough for a quick stop. Parking can be a bit challenging, so keep that in mind when you visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love this place! My husband and I ordered through Snackpass because it was our first time using the app, and I believe we got 5% off — though I’m not entirely sure.\n\nWe ordered the Passion Fruit Mango Icy and Mango & Coconut with Crystal Jelly, and we loved both drinks. The passion fruit mango is perfect for a hot day, especially after a heavy or oily meal — it’s so refreshing and really helps cleanse the palate. The mango & coconut is an amazing combination; the mango and crystal jelly balance out the richness of the coconut perfectly, creating a well-rounded, delicious drink that you have to try. The sweetness is just right — not too sweet, which I really appreciate.\n\nThe shop itself is quite small with limited seating, so it’s more of a pick-up-and-go spot. The service was decent — not over-the-top, but good enough for a quick stop. Parking can be a bit challenging, so keep that in mind when you visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "ahkwai Lert", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107597462103316142932/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWfk0KSPnUofMa0mLFI_rIYGy1H83UetLuk22ZpjemWzhqYg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-21T20:11:43.673227520Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaV1oxUk9iR1JOYVdwQ1JUZGFWVTh4TFZnd2NWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaV1oxUk9iR1JOYVdwQ1JUZGFWVTh4TFZnd2NWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f226875ea89:0x39ff6db4b769d3e5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiep1aCJ_hYAR5dNpt7Rt_zk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aQ2FuQmtjbXgwYW1sbVZtTjBMV3BxVEhoZlduYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "11 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "If you are a mango lover this is your place. I personally love mango.\n\nThey have many mango treat choices so you are sure to find a few you like. The mango’s they use are fresh and ripe! Just the perfect sweetness. Seems all\nOrders are freshly made which is another plus.\n\nThe store is small and they have hardly any service. You order on a tablet and they bring it out and call your name and place it down. Hence no real service.\n\nI went early and the few seats they have were clean. I think this is more of a grab and go sorta place.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "If you are a mango lover this is your place. I personally love mango.\n\nThey have many mango treat choices so you are sure to find a few you like. The mango’s they use are fresh and ripe! Just the perfect sweetness. Seems all\nOrders are freshly made which is another plus.\n\nThe store is small and they have hardly any service. You order on a tablet and they bring it out and call your name and place it down. Hence no real service.\n\nI went early and the few seats they have were clean. I think this is more of a grab and go sorta place.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kristine", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116862894351937962036/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCwauuDqCrpGDoOGNDNJfXQvfzpkxHDPb18_M7LVA3DfRyuLyhIw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-07-21T17:50:58.015505339Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aQ2FuQmtjbXgwYW1sbVZtTjBMV3BxVEhoZlduYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aQ2FuQmtjbXgwYW1sbVZtTjBMV3BxVEhoZlduYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f226875ea89:0x39ff6db4b769d3e5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiep1aCJ_hYAR5dNpt7Rt_zk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKc2FIaGZVakl5WVhjelkwSjFPSGhWVHpGNGFrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "My favorite place of all time for mango treats.  The one time I strayed (ordered a watermelon fresh fruit drink), I regretted it.  It turned out to be mostly ice, cream, tea - in that order. Otherwise the mango desserts and drinks are top notch!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My favorite place of all time for mango treats.  The one time I strayed (ordered a watermelon fresh fruit drink), I regretted it.  It turned out to be mostly ice, cream, tea - in that order. Otherwise the mango desserts and drinks are top notch!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christine C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101329721628864533209/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVu_q82QLk-48Huf57jKvrmy9Gt55c21V2tl1iyWSHOW0oh3r6iqw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-01T03:29:01.160474227Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKc2FIaGZVakl5WVhjelkwSjFPSGhWVHpGNGFrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKc2FIaGZVakl5WVhjelkwSjFPSGhWVHpGNGFrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f226875ea89:0x39ff6db4b769d3e5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiep1aCJ_hYAR5dNpt7Rt_zk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wc1JIbDNORkEwVEVSV1dWOUpXR3BRUW1kclpuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "Not impressed. Neither was the guy’s attitude at the counter when asked what was in one of their trio desserts.\nIt was ok. Ordered mango pancake and one of their bowl desserts (J3 and C4). Desserts were light but nothing to really go out of the way for. Not sure what all the rave is based on other people’s reviews. The pancake is not worth the $8 at all. Take your $20 and just buy a box of fresh yellow mangoes.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Not impressed. Neither was the guy’s attitude at the counter when asked what was in one of their trio desserts.\nIt was ok. Ordered mango pancake and one of their bowl desserts (J3 and C4). Desserts were light but nothing to really go out of the way for. Not sure what all the rave is based on other people’s reviews. The pancake is not worth the $8 at all. Take your $20 and just buy a box of fresh yellow mangoes.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ace C.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114491003632607560187/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhRujwoVOXHwjV2eU8ipDcfZgPwjg6GBRvuMTAdARkMrxa8w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-28T01:36:24.274097550Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wc1JIbDNORkEwVEVSV1dWOUpXR3BRUW1kclpuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wc1JIbDNORkEwVEVSV1dWOUpXR3BRUW1kclpuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f226875ea89:0x39ff6db4b769d3e5"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJiep1aCJ_hYAR5dNpt7Rt_zk/photos/AWCwydgR52SND8L-jaKR7MOBywsjZDfkEJX0RUND4tnAEjo-vEa1zWQH6bnhpHCqff9iw9GsbQmCoDCVLcYSjnlNMdbE0gtJgm70QXaZucp